    <h3>Theme Sample.</h3>
    <hr />
    <h4>1. Setting theme on build-time(static)</h4>
    <p>You can setup a default theme for your app via config.yaml of the app.</p>
    <p>Example config.yaml would look like this:</p>
    <pre>
        appName : Pet Store
        <b>defaultTheme : org.wso2.uuf.theme.default</b>
    </pre>
    <h4>2. Setting theme on runtime(dynamic)</h4>
    <p>You can override your default theme set by config.yaml on the runtime.</p>
    <p>UUF provides two scopes for changing theme during runtime.</p>
    <ol>
        <li>
            Changing theme on <code>application-scope</code>. See the sample <a href="./theme/app-scope"><b>here</b></a>.
        </li>
        <li>
            Changing theme on <code>session-scope</code>. See the sample <a href="./theme/session-scope"><b>here</b></a>.
        </li>
    </ol>
